			</div><p class="getsocial" style="text-align: left;"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;" alt="" src="//getsocialserver.files.wordpress.com/2009/08/gs2001.png" /><a title="Add to Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://wp.me/prlSX-Th" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;" alt="Add to Facebook" src="//getsocialserver.files.wordpress.com/2009/08/gs2011.png" /></a><a title="Add to Digg" href="http://digg.com/submit?phase=2&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.webroot.com%2F2010%2F10%2F04%2Ffive-reasons-you-should-always-stop-think-connect-2&amp;title=Five%20Reasons%20You%20Should%20Always%20Stop.%20Think.%20Connect." target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;" alt="Add to Digg" src="//getsocialserver.files.wordpress.com/2009/08/gs2021.png" /></a><a title="Add to Del.icio.us" href="http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.webroot.com%2F2010%2F10%2F04%2Ffive-reasons-you-should-always-stop-think-connect-2&amp;title=Five%20Reasons%20You%20Should%20Always%20Stop.%20Think.%20Connect." target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;" alt="Add to Del.icio.us" src="//getsocialserver.files.wordpress.com/2009/08/gs2031.png" /></a><a title="Add to Stumbleupon" href="http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.webroot.com%2F2010%2F10%2F04%2Ffive-reasons-you-should-always-stop-think-connect-2&amp;title=Five%20Reasons%20You%20Should%20Always%20Stop.%20Think.%20Connect." target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;" alt="Add to Stumbleupon" src="//getsocialserver.files.wordpress.com/2009/08/gs2041.png" /></a><a title="Add to Reddit" href="http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.webroot.com%2F2010%2F10%2F04%2Ffive-reasons-you-should-always-stop-think-connect-2&amp;title=Five%20Reasons%20You%20Should%20Always%20Stop.%20Think.%20Connect." target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img style="border: 0; margin: 0; padding